{"tid":2339093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"炒散錢途｜Uber、Airbnb未合法 外賣平台唔易撈","createTime":"2020-12-24T11:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T15:32:43.000Z","uid":286146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"80a8d429f7a4e88349d72fb99ffbd51d86f26681","tid":2339093,"uid":286146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T11:32:59.000Z","msg":"睇返條數<br />\nfoodpanda deliveroo同ubereat 根本就圍唔到皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外賣平台疫市彈起 燒錢能撐多久？<br />\n外賣平台收入模式其實並不複雜。綜合市場數據，各平台平均向合作食肆收取每張訂單約30%為佣金，另收客戶14元送餐費；「車手」或「步兵」每完成一單柯打，平均賺約45元。換句話說，如果訂單金額不高，外賣平台便要蝕住做（見下表）。<span class=\"red\">此外他們得承擔訂單賠償、客戶服務、應用程式開發、市場推廣、保險和辦公室租金等開支，</span>結果為了控制成本調整政策而得常罪合作夥伴。平衡各方利益並建立良好形象，是所有企業的永恒要務，外賣平台雖屬「零工經濟」亦無例外，前面挑戰不小。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0OsWsL3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0OsWsL3.png&h=35c3bd59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201224/R3ZOWB3LNNATXGWOJQ5N7IBBEY/?fbclid=IwAR0II0vvT-HK2WNWAFESmr2fZX_XYuAdap3u6jodx49zmfu1rfyZb4VQ81c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201224%2FR3ZOWB3LNNATXGWOJQ5N7IBBEY%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0II0vvT-HK2WNWAFESmr2fZX_XYuAdap3u6jodx49zmfu1rfyZb4VQ81c&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt5uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=29c88494\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201224%2FR3ZOWB3LNNATXGWOJQ5N7IBBEY%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0II0vvT-HK2WNWAFESmr2fZX_XYuAdap3u6jodx49zmfu1rfyZb4VQ81c&h=9c42ed38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201224/R3ZOWB3LNNATXGWOJQ5N7IBBEY/?fbclid=IwAR0II0vvT-HK2WNWAFESmr2fZX_XYuAdap3u6jodx49zmfu1rfyZb4VQ81c</a>"},{"pid":"66e6cc1d886087fbf254cce6ffc8f9ed02084503","tid":2339093,"uid":7179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:38:43.000Z","msg":"啲外賣仔咪無野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b08f6f1bb5358eef78ece9d737fd265c1ec2d8","tid":2339093,"uid":158546,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:48:47.000Z","msg":"送餐費唔係起碼$20？<br />\n同埋經apps叫得嘅野食，餐廳定價九成都唔止$60"},{"pid":"188402f35a88435899ccd743ffa0f28d46ba948c","tid":2339093,"uid":22390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:32:43.000Z","msg":"我都想有45<br />\n<br />\n大概係抽3成 運費收個客幾多就平台食曬<br />\n100以下單通常都蝕住做<br />\n步兵大概30 車手大概50<br />\n宜家咁多人做好難搵食了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}